Text.string: This whole “Crimson Raiders” thing would totally fall apart without me: Claptrap!
Well done, recruit. I can tell you're gonna do good work for me.
Just so you know, getting caught by that magnet was allll part of the plan.
The Children of the Vault have made Pandora EVEN WORSE!
If we don't stop the Children of the Vault, they'll turn all of Pandora into one huge murder party. I mean, moreso than it already was!
Way to shut up that jerk Mouthpiece! I would've done it myself, but I was super busy with other stuff.
You, uh... you think Lilith is gonna be okay?
Space travel, Vault Hunter! SPACE TRAVEL!
I'm gonna run this ship some day. Mark my words!
I hear Promethea is like one giant city! I can't wait to see it!
Well, at least we took down Troy Calypso. One down, one to go! I'd say that's progress!
Wow. Typhon DeLeon: the FIRST Vault Hunter! Let me know if he wants my autograph. But he's gotta pay like everybody else.
Nekrotafeyo is REAL?! Is it... is it full of monsters?

I can hardly believe that Ava is a freakin' Siren now! Really makes you think. The universe is a strange, magical place... even if it's also full of things that are always trying to kill you or turn you into a torture toy.
So Typhon's been stranded on Nekrotafeyo for thirty years? That sounds... AWESOME! I could really use a vacation from you losers.
What a REVELATION! Typhon is the Calypsos' FATHER! Can you even BELIEVE THAT?!||—Totally saw it coming.
You think this Machine thing will really save the galaxy? Well, it better! Or I'm gonna give Typhon DeLeon a piece of my mind!
Maliwan found Nekrotafeyo too? We just can't get rid of those guys, can we?
Boy, Typhon's just FULL of surprises, isn't he?
She just killed him! Her own father! I mean, I knew Tyreen was a monster, but this... this is a new low, even for her.
Man, Tyreen is so powerful! She took out our team, Typhon, AND the Machine in one attack! We're doomed! I know it! We're totally boned-to-the-max DOOMED!
I'm okay! I'm not freaking out. YOU'RE freaking out! Someone needs to keep a clear head around here!
What kind of monstrosity do you think Tyreen will turn into?
If Tyreen really becomes a god... what do you think she'll do next?
Well, we succeeded, recruit. All thanks to my strong, guiding hand. You're welcome.
I thought the destroyer was scary BEFORE it fused with a power-hungry Siren with delusions of godhood. Wow-ee. But you just rushed headlong into danger and took it out! Just like I trained you.
Mark another heroic victory for Claptrap! And, uh, the Crimson Raiders too, I guess.
Do you think we'll ever see Lilith again? I never told her how much her loyalty meant to me.
Okay, fine. Lilith was more heroic than me... but just this one time!
You too, huh? Everybody wants a piece of old Claptrap!
Plpth, pth, a-plbth-plthb-pthlb, doo-doo-duh bop, doo-doo bop bop bah! A-blpth-doo-bplth-da-chaaa!
[sigh] I wish I could wear pants.
It's hard not having anyone to look up to the way you look up to me. I guess that's just the cost of being perfect.
There's no good way to say this so I'm just gonna come right out with it. “On root”? “In rout”? WHICH IS IT?!
You met Zer0?! That guy is almost as cool as me!
That Katagawa guy is a real super-douche!
Do you think I'd look good with a mustache like Rhys? I bet I would.
The Crimson Raiders, aligning with a corporation? Why wasn't I consulted?
Rhys sure turned Atlas around! It was a real pee-yew stink-mess for a while there. What a comeback!
Athenas seems like it's probably a nice place when it's not being invaded.
Ava is officially my new favorite. Screw you, everybody else!
Those monks are WIMPS. If I was down on Athenas, I'd kick Maliwan's asses all over the place!
Those COV sure get around.
You're doing a great job getting under Katagawa's skin! Also, skin is gross.
Way to take out those Maliwan goons, Vault Hunter!
Katagawa got exactly what was coming to him: a swift kick in the soft bits!
Looks like it's time to open that Vault! Just remember, if you die—I get all your stuff.
The universe has one less super-douche to deal with!
Way to save Atlas from those Maliwan jerks!
Now that Katagawa's dead, maybe Promethea will go back to normal. But I wouldn't hold my breath—even if I could.
Maya... once, she threatened to throw me out the airlock. And now she's GONE!
Those Calypsos are monsters! And not the good kind! There are good monsters, right? Right?
Look, I'm just gonna say this. Troy Calypso is not very nice. It HAD to be said.
Troy and Tyreen are even stronger than they were before. This doesn't bode well. It bodes bad! Bodes real bad!
I hope my best friend Ava's doing okay. Maybe one of my incredibly long stories about my thrilling exploits would cheer her up! It always does for me!
Just between us, I'm actually TERRIFIED of Tina! I think she wants to turn me into a bomb. 'Cause she wouldn't stop saying it!
You know what? I'll let YOU handle things down on Eden-6. Those swamplands would really gunk up my gears, and I'm NOT just making excuses!
It's good to see the B-Team still kicking ass and using an unreasonable amount of explosives!
Eden-6 was known as a paradise planet. How's it holding up?
The Jakobs family has been on Eden-6 for a LONG time. You'd think the place wouldn't be so... rustic. And by “rustic”, I mean “a backwater hellhole from which there is no escape”!
Me and Aurelia go way, way back. And I've hated her the whole time! And I'm NOT just saying that in light of recent events!
You're starting the Jakobs resistance? Fantastic! I'll grab my rhyming dictionary so we can come up with some killer chants!
How's that Jakobs resistance thing going for you?
So, Aurelia's working with the Calypsos, huh? That's a new low, even for her.
Damn that Troy! I'm so sick of his smug, stupid face! I swear, if he commits one more atrocity, I'm gonna unsubscribe from his ECHOcasts.
Aww, crap. We gotta go back to Pandora? But I have so many painful memories back there! Physically painful!
I sure hope Tannis is okay! Even if she does refer to me as a rolling trash can with no conceivable utility or purpose. Tannis... stay safe!
Aurelia finally got what was comin' to her, eh? I wonder if she put me in her will like she said she would.
Those dastardly Calypsos! What dastardly deeds might they do next?! DASTARDLY!
The COV are still running wild all over Pandora. Be careful back there!
Tannis is a SIREN?! What'll we find out next? Brick's a ballerina?! Actually, I can totally see that. He's pretty graceful for a gargantuan meatslab of a man.
It's time, recruit. I'm ordering you to take down those Calypsos! Don't screw it up! Dismissed!
This is the big one, recruit! I know you're up to it! I'd help you out with all my murderous skills, but I've really gotta keep an eye on the ship. You understand.
Imagine driving that massive Carnivora deathwagon! The power! The glory! On a totally unrelated note, my birthday is coming up.
For the record, I'm just as deadly as that Agonizer thing you smashed. I just like to keep it under wraps so I don't scare the others. But don't cross me!
Way to take down Shiv, recruit! I knew you had it in you!
Oooh, time to track down that long-lost Vault Map, huh?
Hammerlock's free?! That's great! Don't look into it, but we're SUPER good friends.
I'm gonna have a mansion like that some day, just you wait!
I always did love a good uprising.
Well THAT was a real trip. I'm glad BALEX came out on top.
Oooh, you did a secret infiltration mission? Cool!
Tannis may ignore me whenever possible, but we need to get her back anyway! For reasons!
Plug me into that Carnivora thing and I'll rule the Pandoran wasteland under my giant wheels!
Troy, meet Death. Death, Troy.
Typhon's my new hero, just so you know. Heroes come in all shapes and sizes, he says! And “all shapes” includes trapezoidal!
She BROKE THE MACHINE?! Awww, crap. We're doomed again! Doomed! AGAIN! I mean, uhhhh, it's time to fight! For YOU to fight! Go get 'er, chief!
Those Calypsos are terrifying! Hoooly crap!
The universe is saved thanks to us, recruit. I just wish Lilith were here to celebrate this victory with us.
Hey recruit—what are you doing working for Tannis? You're my bitch... ing best friend! Saved it!
It's time. Everything I've taught you will be put to the test, recruit. Do not fail me.
It's a good thing I can't feel boredom because YOWZA!
Have you had a chance to check out my mixtape yet?
So, Mercenary Day will be here before you know it. Thought about what you're gonna get me?
Guess it's LOTS of rest for the wicked, huh?
Hey, recruit! Drop and give me twenty dollars! That's an order!
We're gonna get Tyreen for what she did! Right, recruit?
Sanctuary is ready to blast off! Woo!
Crimson Raiders: ROLL OUT!
Looks like Maya hasn't slowed down a bit! Bam! Badass incoming!
You really nailed Katagawa's junk with that space laser!
Annnnd Katagawa is OUTTA HERE! Gahahahaha!
Maya... I can't believe it.
I know you're busy, but—friendly reminder—you could totally be busier.
Hey, I've got an idea! DO THE THING I TOLD YOU TO DO!
Yoo-hoooo! I've got a job for yooou...
Hi!
Hello, traveler!
Howdy, recruit!
Hey! Hi! How are you?
Hey there!
I've got a mission for you, recruit!
Do my bidding, recruit!
Ready for another mission?
Mission for you!
Time to kick some ass!
How's my mission going?
You taking care of that thing?
Doing that thing, recruit?
How's that job coming?
Gettin' it done?
Oh, okay. Bye!
Uhhhh, toodles?
See ya later!
Bye!
Okay, we'll talk later.
Hmph.
Yep.
All right.
I'll be right here if you need me.
Okay.
